{"barInfo":{"barName":"骁","description":"开放自由的类贴吧式留言板","isMainBar":true,"isPublic":true},"list":[{"author":"xingyux1","authorCode":"CBA2C10357","content":"<p>我这里说的“数字生命”并不像电影里的那么高大上，它其实就是一个在大模型基础上训练的LORA。</p><p>写过的文章、随记、个人资料、聊天记录甚至是内心的想法<span style=\"color:rgb(18, 18, 18);\">都可以用作训练</span>LORA<span style=\"color:rgb(18, 18, 18);\">的素材。</span></p><p><span style=\"color:rgb(18, 18, 18);\">做这个</span>LORA<span style=\"color:rgb(18, 18, 18);\">有两个好处</span></p><p>1.如果人还在健在，那么这个就可以当做自己当时的思想的一个副本，时隔多年以后自己遇到问题了可以通过这个看看自己当年面对这些事情会怎么想/怎么做。</p><p><span style=\"color:rgb(18, 18, 18);\">2.如果人不幸故去了，那么亲人和朋友可以通过这个</span>LORA来怀念他，其在语言/处理事情的风格上会和本人很相似，如果是遇到了问题也可以通过这个进行询问（比如：这件事如果是他在的话他会怎么做？）。</p><p>制作这个LORA主要需要两个东西：资料和算力。</p><p>资料的话你有很多随记很多文章，这些是现成的。</p><p>算力的话据我所知知乎的<span style=\"color:rgb(18, 18, 18);\">PENG Bo（</span><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/bopengbopeng\" target=\"_blank\">PENG Bo - 知乎 (zhihu.com)</a><span style=\"color:rgb(18, 18, 18);\">）有足够的算力而且他也很想去推动他开发的RWKV模型，如果你想的话我可以帮你问问。你和他都是计算机出身，对接起来应该会比我懂得多。</span></p>","floor":1,"pid":0,"postTime":"2023-07-11 14:08:04","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","sourceUrl":"","tid":3231},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>害……先容我消化一下</p>","floor":2,"pid":9048,"postTime":"2023-07-11 18:15:04","replyCount":1,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":3231,"initComments":{"list":[{"author":"xingyux1","authorCode":"CBA2C10357","content":"你可以看看\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/answer/2835179135\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhihu.com/answer/2835179135</a>\n<a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/620327907\" target=\"_blank\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/620327907</a>\n<a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/638326262\" target=\"_blank\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/638326262</a>\n","createTime":"2023-07-11 18:45:43","id":5498,"replyId":null,"replyUserCode":"","authorInfo":{"exists":true,"name":"xingyux1","code":"CBA2C10357","alias":"","description":"网友","homepageUrl":"/u/CBA2C10357","group":2,"groupName":"实名用户","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/common/person.jpg","realName":"邢雨","refBaike":"","isManager":false,"isMe":false,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2018-06-18 21:20:43"}}],"pageInfo":{"total":1,"pageSize":10,"current":1},"total":1,"totalPages":1}},{"author":"xingyux1","authorCode":"CBA2C10357","content":"<p>除了<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 102, 102);\">文章、随记之类，你自己的程序代码也是可以训练到lora里的，到时候生成的“数字生命”代码风格也会很像你。现在的大模型基本上都会编写代码了。</span></p><p><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 102, 102);\">这个大模型你可以理解为一个广义上的“人”，就像chatgpt那样是一个助手而没有自己的性格，lora则是通过外加的资料进行补充训练，将人的特色从文字资料里赋予到其中，这样组合起来就会有这个人的独特性格/风格。</span></p><p>而你做lora最大的便捷之处是：1.很少有人能像你这样十年一日的记录生活，资料十分充足。2.你懂编程懂技术，这些对你来说不是难事。</p><p>这个不仅对于自己或者亲人有意义，对于学术上可能也会有作用，就像当年的<span style=\"color:rgb(51, 51, 51);\">海拉细胞一样可以在对应领域发光发热。</span></p>","floor":3,"pid":9049,"postTime":"2023-07-11 19:21:07","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":3231},{"author":"106.8.142.*","authorCode":"","content":"<p>我只能说……我不认为留下数字生命是什么好主意。</p>","floor":4,"pid":9072,"postTime":"2023-07-18 18:19:44","replyCount":7,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":3231,"initComments":{"list":[{"author":"Sunbread","authorCode":"FD5F2BEFEC","content":"如果需要联系的话我可以帮忙联系，不过我不认为数字生命是什么好主意，我也不认为bo会认为这是什么好主意。","createTime":"2023-07-18 18:21:54","id":5521,"replyId":null,"replyUserCode":"","authorInfo":{"exists":true,"name":"Sunbread","code":"FD5F2BEFEC","alias":"smm","description":"面包君","homepageUrl":"/u/smm","group":1,"groupName":"认证用户","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/user/cfda1a1be4d5.jpg","realName":"孙某某","refBaike":"","isManager":false,"isMe":false,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2015-04-08 05:01:41"}},{"author":"xingyux1","authorCode":"CBA2C10357","content":"我是列举了几个我觉得有意义的地方，如果你觉得不是什么好主意，可以列列数字生命的缺点，然后去权衡一下。","createTime":"2023-07-18 20:04:20","id":5524,"replyId":null,"replyUserCode":"","authorInfo":{"exists":true,"name":"xingyux1","code":"CBA2C10357","alias":"","description":"网友","homepageUrl":"/u/CBA2C10357","group":2,"groupName":"实名用户","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/common/person.jpg","realName":"邢雨","refBaike":"","isManager":false,"isMe":false,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2018-06-18 21:20:43"}},{"author":"Sunbread","authorCode":"FD5F2BEFEC","content":"并不是数字生命的缺点，而是就我所知LLM和一个可以堪称助理的数字生命之间尚有较大差距，更不要提作为可以对等交流的人格了。","createTime":"2023-07-18 20:27:30","id":5525,"replyId":5524,"replyUserCode":"CBA2C10357","authorInfo":{"exists":true,"name":"Sunbread","code":"FD5F2BEFEC","alias":"smm","description":"面包君","homepageUrl":"/u/smm","group":1,"groupName":"认证用户","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/user/cfda1a1be4d5.jpg","realName":"孙某某","refBaike":"","isManager":false,"isMe":false,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2015-04-08 05:01:41"},"replyUserInfo":{"exists":true,"name":"xingyux1","code":"CBA2C10357","alias":"","description":"网友","homepageUrl":"/u/CBA2C10357","group":2,"groupName":"实名用户","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/common/person.jpg","realName":"邢雨","refBaike":"","isManager":false,"isMe":false,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2018-06-18 21:20:43"}},{"author":"Sunbread","authorCode":"FD5F2BEFEC","content":"LLM幻觉非常严重。为了克服幻觉问题，必须进行针对语料的加强，但这又会带来灾难性遗忘问题，模型的输出会失去原主风格。","createTime":"2023-07-18 20:28:27","id":5526,"replyId":5524,"replyUserCode":"CBA2C10357","authorInfo":{"exists":true,"name":"Sunbread","code":"FD5F2BEFEC","alias":"smm","description":"面包君","homepageUrl":"/u/smm","group":1,"groupName":"认证用户","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/user/cfda1a1be4d5.jpg","realName":"孙某某","refBaike":"","isManager":false,"isMe":false,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2015-04-08 05:01:41"},"replyUserInfo":{"exists":true,"name":"xingyux1","code":"CBA2C10357","alias":"","description":"网友","homepageUrl":"/u/CBA2C10357","group":2,"groupName":"实名用户","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/common/person.jpg","realName":"邢雨","refBaike":"","isManager":false,"isMe":false,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2018-06-18 21:20:43"}},{"author":"Sunbread","authorCode":"FD5F2BEFEC","content":"另一方面，bo作为rwkv实质上的精神领袖，让他帮忙训练人的资料，对rwkv社区发展非常有害。我更建议去一些提供AI机器租赁的网站购买GPU时间自己训练。","createTime":"2023-07-18 20:29:30","id":5527,"replyId":5524,"replyUserCode":"CBA2C10357","authorInfo":{"exists":true,"name":"Sunbread","code":"FD5F2BEFEC","alias":"smm","description":"面包君","homepageUrl":"/u/smm","group":1,"groupName":"认证用户","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/user/cfda1a1be4d5.jpg","realName":"孙某某","refBaike":"","isManager":false,"isMe":false,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2015-04-08 05:01:41"},"replyUserInfo":{"exists":true,"name":"xingyux1","code":"CBA2C10357","alias":"","description":"网友","homepageUrl":"/u/CBA2C10357","group":2,"groupName":"实名用户","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/common/person.jpg","realName":"邢雨","refBaike":"","isManager":false,"isMe":false,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2018-06-18 21:20:43"}},{"author":"Sunbread","authorCode":"FD5F2BEFEC","content":"当然你也可以去问问bo。不过就我对他的了解，他很忙且性格比较暴躁。","createTime":"2023-07-18 20:30:03","id":5528,"replyId":5524,"replyUserCode":"CBA2C10357","authorInfo":{"exists":true,"name":"Sunbread","code":"FD5F2BEFEC","alias":"smm","description":"面包君","homepageUrl":"/u/smm","group":1,"groupName":"认证用户","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/user/cfda1a1be4d5.jpg","realName":"孙某某","refBaike":"","isManager":false,"isMe":false,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2015-04-08 05:01:41"},"replyUserInfo":{"exists":true,"name":"xingyux1","code":"CBA2C10357","alias":"","description":"网友","homepageUrl":"/u/CBA2C10357","group":2,"groupName":"实名用户","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/common/person.jpg","realName":"邢雨","refBaike":"","isManager":false,"isMe":false,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2018-06-18 21:20:43"}},{"author":"xingyux1","authorCode":"CBA2C10357","content":"没单独和他交流过，不过我在群里看他性格还算平和的，可能是我不了解吧。简而言之就是技术上还差点火候，不过我认为饭一口一口吃，先是个小lora然后逐渐建立数字生命，就像晓哥的网站一样，这么多年笔耕不辍。","createTime":"2023-07-18 20:56:36","id":5529,"replyId":null,"rep